====Verb====
{{en-verb|abrad}}

# {{lb|en|transitive}} To [[rub off|rub]] or [[wear off]]; [[erode]]. {{defdate|First attested in the late 17<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED>{{R:SOED5|page=7}}</ref>
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To wear down or exhaust, as a person; [[irritate]]. {{defdate|First attested in the mid 18<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To irritate by rubbing; [[chafe]]. {{defdate|First attested in the mid 18<sup>th</sup> century.}}<ref name=SOED/>
# {{lb|en|transitive}} To cause the surface to become more rough.
# {{lb|en|intransitive}} To undergo [[abrasion]].

